tftp_firmware_writer

Simple program to write firmware on router

BUILD:
gcc -Wall tftp_firmare_writer.c -o tftp_firmare_writer

USAGE:
-h - for help
Porgram listen UDP port (69),
and reply with firmware_file to RPQ request.

For my router - TL-WR841ND(ver 8.4)
tftp_firmare_writer -b 192.168.0.66 /home/k.kogdenko/Downloads/mr3420v2_tp_recovery.bin
and press reset button
